{"tid":1709693,"cid":5,"subCid":10,"title":"旺角水炮車射藥房　男子擲物還擊　警員正面近距離開胡椒槍拘捕","createTime":"2019-11-12T03:04:40.000Z","updateTime":"2019-11-16T21:18:54.000Z","uid":23707,"like":243,"dislike":4,"uniUserReply":88,"replies":[{"pid":"aa5a74cde20dc1d0183963e58e99feec8a920512","tid":1709693,"uid":23707,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-11-12T03:04:40.000Z","msg":"<a href=\"https://www.thestandnews.com/politics/%E7%9D%87%E7%89%87-%E6%97%BA%E8%A7%92%E6%B0%B4%E7%82%AE%E8%BB%8A%E5%B0%84%E8%97%A5%E6%88%BF-%E7%94%B7%E5%AD%90%E6%93%B2%E7%89%A9%E9%82%84%E6%93%8A-%E8%AD%A6%E5%93%A1%E6%AD%A3%E9%9D%A2%E8%BF%91%E8%B7%9D%E9%9B%A2%E9%96%8B%E8%83%A1%E6%A4%92%E6%A7%8D%E6%8B%98%E6%8D%95/\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fwww.thestandnews.com%2Fpolitics%2F%25E7%259D%2587%25E7%2589%2587-%25E6%2597%25BA%25E8%25A7%2592%25E6%25B0%25B4%25E7%2582%25AE%25E8%25BB%258A%25E5%25B0%2584%25E8%2597%25A5%25E6%2588%25BF-%25E7%2594%25B7%25E5%25AD%2590%25E6%2593%25B2%25E7%2589%25A9%25E9%2582%2584%25E6%2593%258A-%25E8%25AD%25A6%25E5%2593%25A1%25E6%25AD%25A3%25E9%259D%25A2%25E8%25BF%2591%25E8%25B7%259D%25E9%259B%25A2%25E9%2596%258B%25E8%2583%25A1%25E6%25A4%2592%25E6%25A7%258D%25E6%258B%2598%25E6%258D%2595%2F&d=4awEA7knrPrnmlrQXGUFYoRM%2FwdnRWUJBfohchWxIRY%3D&h=fff5b305\" data-ef-url=\"https://embed.lih.kg/frame?u=https%3A%2F%2Fwww.thestandnews.com%2Fpolitics%2F%25E7%259D%2587%25E7%2589%2587-%25E6%2597%25BA%25E8%25A7%2592%25E6%25B0%25B4%25E7%2582%25AE%25E8%25BB%258A%25E5%25B0%2584%25E8%2597%25A5%25E6%2588%25BF-%25E7%2594%25B7%25E5%25AD%2590%25E6%2593%25B2%25E7%2589%25A9%25E9%2582%2584%25E6%2593%258A-%25E8%25AD%25A6%25E5%2593%25A1%25E6%25AD%25A3%25E9%259D%25A2%25E8%25BF%2591%25E8%25B7%259D%25E9%259B%25A2%25E9%2596%258B%25E8%2583%25A1%25E6%25A4%2592%25E6%25A7%258D%25E6%258B%2598%25E6%258D%2595%2F&h=3552cb2f\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://www.thestandnews.com/politics/%E7%9D%87%E7%89%87-%E6%97%BA%E8%A7%92%E6%B0%B4%E7%82%AE%E8%BB%8A%E5%B0%84%E8%97%A5%E6%88%BF-%E7%94%B7%E5%AD%90%E6%93%B2%E7%89%A9%E9%82%84%E6%93%8A-%E8%AD%A6%E5%93%A1%E6%AD%A3%E9%9D%A2%E8%BF%91%E8%B7%9D%E9%9B%A2%E9%96%8B%E8%83%A1%E6%A4%92%E6%A7%8D%E6%8B%98%E6%8D%95/</a><br />\n<br />\n昨晚警方出動水炮車驅散在油尖旺一帶的示威者，太子一間藥房的貨品被水炮射濕，引起疑似藥房職員不滿，以藥房貨品擲向水炮車，之後多名防暴警員到場制服該男子，又以胡椒球槍向不足一米距離的男子正面發射。該男子最後被捕。<br />\n<br />\n昨晚 10 時許，警方水炮車駛到彌敦道北行線弼街交界位置，控制員將水炮射上行人路，噴射到「金城免稅藥坊」店門，門口的貨品亦告遭殃。之後，有一名職員從店內拿出貨品，擲向馬路上的水炮車。<br />\n<br />\n水炮車離開之後，職員開始執拾貨品，突然有 4 名防暴警員衝向職員位置，職員嘗試用手撥開警員，結果一名警員以胡椒球槍指向職員，並且在距離職員 3 呎的範圍內，向職員發射胡椒球彈。最後藥房職員被多名警員按在地上制服和拘捕。<br />\n<br />\n水炮射中記者<br />\n<br />\n另外，水炮車昨晚亦在彌敦道和亞皆老街交界發射水炮，惟不只一次射中記者。《城市廣播》昨晚 8 時許拍攝到水炮車曾經在彌敦道和亞皆老街交界的恒生銀行分行外停留，及後突然發射水炮，多名記者走避不及，全身被射濕甚至擊中滑倒地上，部分記者則走到銀行內，或者行人路的電話亭躲避，而當時行人路上未見有示威者。<br />\n<br />\n之後，水炮車亦將水炮射向對面行車線的九巴雙層巴士，當時巴士內仍然有多名乘客。"},{"pid":"e26feb1323889a7b8077170c4e07b67de4211930","tid":1709693,"uid":24853,"like":25,"dislike":0,"score":25,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-11-12T03:06:31.000Z","msg":"藥房"},{"pid":"8c87162a4611fe6067287d02488f99067fdeecb5","tid":1709693,"uid":144883,"like":18,"dislike":0,"score":18,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-11-12T03:06:49.000Z","msg":"藥房<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/smile.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"15c434ca6b745a0a6985dbf8f0e95a06a7854157","tid":1709693,"uid":177047,"like":40,"dislike":0,"score":40,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-11-12T03:09:10.000Z","msg":"實比人屈毒品拆家"},{"pid":"221225b7b0beb5af10fa04f3bfc3fbb26c3330a8","tid":1709693,"uid":123591,"like":26,"dislike":0,"score":26,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-11-12T03:10:24.000Z","msg":"分分鐘比人屈賣咳藥水<img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/scare.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"c68ce301ccaefc250c735786f1b73ec13d390c7a","tid":1709693,"uid":254594,"like":71,"dislike":1,"score":70,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-11-12T03:10:26.000Z","msg":"最唔想connect的<br />\n可能被逼connect了<img src=\"/assets/faces/fs/smile.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"97f531a0f4c0af21a77bba96c98a4d1d556f4123","tid":1709693,"uid":287387,"like":60,"dislike":0,"score":60,"citedBy":2,"replyTime"